Class EventDefListAllHandler

java.lang.Object
  nl.vumc.trait.oc.soap.EventDefListAllHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.xml.ws.handler.Handler<javax.xml.ws.handler.soap.SOAPMessageContext>, javax.xml.ws.handler.soap.SOAPHandler<javax.xml.ws.handler.soap.SOAPMessageContext>
public class EventDefListAllHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.xml.ws.handler.soap.SOAPHandler<javax.xml.ws.handler.soap.SOAPMessageContext>

This handler renames nodes that belong to the beans http://openclinica.org/ws/beans but that are incorrectly returned in the wrong namespace by OpenClinica 3.1.2-community. See issue report 13333 (https://issuetracker.openclinica.com/view.php?id=13333).

Author:
Arjan van der Velde (ag.vandervelde@vumc.nl)
